    "role": "Aeroelastic analysis team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "OpenFAST DEL predictions at blade root show less than 8% deviation from field-measured strain-gauge data across 6 wind speed bins. Simulation conservatively overpredicts loads. Adequate for DLC 1.1 fatigue sizing per IEC 61400-1.",
